title: Bohtell man wanted for using truck as weapon in altercation...
text:
Officials are searching for a man suspected for using his truck as a weapon in an altercation with a relative last night.
Mark D. Grenell is wanted for Domestic Assault first degree.
Suspect Mark D. Grenell is wanted for DV Assault 1st Degree; using his truck as a weapon. Call BPD if spotted pic.twitter.com/gakphxTGQu
— Bothell Police (@BothellPolice) October 25, 2015 Bothell Police report non-life-threatening injuries to an adult male. The male was transported to the hospital.
The altercation occurred at the 7-11 in Thrasher’s Corner, near SR 527 and Maltby Road.
The investigation is ongoing.
